import React from "react";
import { Box, FormControl, InputLabel, Select, MenuItem, Button } from "@mui/material";

export default function DiodeForm({ diodeType, setDiodeType, mode, setMode, onGenerate }) {
  return (
    <Box display="flex" justifyContent="center" gap={2} flexWrap="wrap" marginBottom={2}>
      
      <FormControl sx={{ minWidth: 180 }}>
        <InputLabel>Diode Type</InputLabel>
        <Select value={diodeType} label="Diode Type" onChange={(e) => setDiodeType(e.target.value)}>
          <MenuItem value="silicon">Silicon</MenuItem>
          <MenuItem value="germanium">Germanium</MenuItem>
          <MenuItem value="led">LED</MenuItem>
          <MenuItem value="zener">Zener</MenuItem>
        </Select>
      </FormControl>

      <FormControl sx={{ minWidth: 180 }}>
        <InputLabel>Bias Mode</InputLabel>
        <Select value={mode} label="Bias Mode" onChange={(e) => setMode(e.target.value)}>
          <MenuItem value="forward">Forward Bias</MenuItem>
          <MenuItem value="reverse">Reverse Bias</MenuItem>
        </Select>
      </FormControl>

      <Button variant="contained" size="large" sx={{ textTransform: "none" }} onClick={onGenerate}>
        Generate Graph
      </Button>

    </Box>
  );
}
